> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/pagehide_event\"><code>pagehide</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/pageshow_event\"><code>pageshow</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/paste_event\"><code>paste</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Window/popstate_event\"><code>popstate</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/rejectionhandled_event\"><code>rejectionhandled</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/storage_event\"><code>storage</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/unhandledrejection_event\"><code>unhandledrejection</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/unload_event\"><code>unload</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplayactivate_event\"><code>vrdisplayactivate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplayblur_event\"><code>vrdisplayblur</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplayconnect_event\"><code>vrdisplayconnect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaydeactivate_event\"><code>vrdisplaydeactivate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaydisconnect_event\"><code>vrdisplaydisconnect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplayfocus_event\"><code>vrdisplayfocus</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaypointerrestricted_event\"><code>vrdisplaypointerrestricted</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaypointerunrestricted_event\"><code>vrdisplaypointerunrestricted</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaypresentchange_event\"><code>vrdisplaypresentchange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Herencia</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"resumen","title":"Resumen","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Devuelve un objeto de selección representando el rango del texto seleccionado por el usuario. <span class=\"comment\">NB. this is nothing to do with the DOM selection list object! What the heck is 'selection list object'? -Nickolay</span></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxis","title":"Sintaxis","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\"><em>selection</em> =<em>window</em>.getSelection()&nbsp;;\n</pre>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code>selection</code> es un objeto de <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Selection\">selección</a>.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ejemplo","title":"Ejemplo","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">function foo() {\n   var selObj = window.getSelection();\n   alert(selObj);\n   var selRange = selObj.getRangeAt(0);\n   // ... Hacer las cosas con el rango ...\n}\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notas","title":"Notas","isH3":true,"content":"<p>En JavaScript, cuando un objeto de selección es pasado a una función que espera una cadena de caracteres como parámetro (como <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Window/alert\"><code>window.alert</code></a> o <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Document/write\"><code>document.write</code></a>), una representación de texto, del objeto de selección (e.j. el texto seleccionado) es pasado en vez del objeto en sí. Esto hace al objeto de selección parecer una cadena de caracteres (texto), cuando realmente es un objeto con sus propios métodos y propiedades. Específicamente, el valor de retorno de llamar al método <code><a href=\"es/DOM/Selection/toString\">toString()</a></code> del objeto de selección es lo que realmente se pasa como parámetro a la función.</p>\n\n<p>En el ejemplo de arriba, <code>selObj</code> es automaticamente \"convertido\" cuando pasó a <a href=\"es/DOM/window.alert\">window.alert</a>. Sin embargo, para usar una propiedad <a href=\"es/JS/String\">String</a> de JavaScript o un método como <code><a href=\"es/JS/String.prototype.length\">length</a></code> o <code><a href=\"es/JS/String.prototype.substr\">substr</a></code>, debe llamar manualmente al método <code>toString</code>. <span class=\"comment\">I'm treading carefully with the word \"convert\" here because it could be misinterpreted as a permanent convert - Maian</span></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificaci.c3.b3n","title":"Especificación","isH3":true,"content":"<p>DOM Nivel 0. No es parte de ninguna especificación.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ver_tambi.c3.a9n","title":"Ver también","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a href=\"es/docs/Web/API/Selection\">Selection</a>, <a href=\"es/docs/Web/API/Range\">Range</a></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"noinclude\" id=\"sect2\"></div>\n\n<p></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"Devuelve un objeto de selección representando el rango del texto seleccionado por el usuario. NB. this is nothing to do with the DOM selection list object! What the heck is 'selection list object'? -Nickolay","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Window.getSelection()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"window.getSelection","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"window.getSelection","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Window.getSelection()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"window.getSelection","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Window.getSelection()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Window.getSelection()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Window.getSelection","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"es/web/api/window/getselection","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/es/web/api/window/getselection/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/es/docs/Web","title":"Tecnología para desarrolladores web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API","title":"Referencia de la API Web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API/Window","title":"window"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/API/Window/getSelection","title":"window.getSelection"}],"pageTitle":"window.getSelection - Referencia de la API Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}